Invocation Name: farm day trip
des:
This is an interactive story adventure of a young boy and a young girl, going on a day trip to the local farm in Ireland with their dad. They come across several animal noises and have to guess what they have encountered. 
We hope you enjoy this story, if you do. Please leave a rating so we can continue to make many more adventures like this.

Parental approval required
